{"tid":961194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"富士康將在印度組裝貴價IPhone　　避中美貿易戰！","createTime":"2018-12-30T01:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T00:06:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5ea2d1c2abae0251e9dce455543e7d90b38430","tid":961194,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T01:42:17.000Z","msg":"富士康將在印度組裝貴價IPhone　　避中美貿易戰！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/12/foxconn-high-end-iphone-assembling-in-india/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F12%2Ffoxconn-high-end-iphone-assembling-in-india%2F&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=261acd12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/12/foxconn-high-end-iphone-assembling-in-india/</a><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰似乎有排玩，雙方何時才會讓步，暫時難以清楚。本身在大陸組裝的iPhone，蘋果決定把貴價的系列，包括iPhone XS等，都搬到去印度組裝。目前iPhone SE和iPhone 6S已經在印度組裝，若果連iPhone XS等貴價都搬到印度，將有效避過持續惡化的中美貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">富士康目前已在印度替小米組裝手機，未來他們也打算加重在印度的投資，為當地建立25,000職位空缺。</span>由於富士康和蘋果都拒絕評論，暫未知道富士康是否把所有大陸的生產搬到印度。他們過往其實也有考慮過中國大陸以外不少的地方，包括越南等。"},{"pid":"f63bfa89fbbce95953769544250c5339c49b623b","tid":961194,"uid":193364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T01:43:54.000Z","msg":"連屌米都係印度組裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f3621d30046fa3ff802c69bdce1581cade6b94","tid":961194,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"又贏，呢d低技術組裝工快d搬出中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfecb10083e07d691574362bfa269a59eb7228e","tid":961194,"uid":28195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T01:46:58.000Z","msg":"中國可以接高技術工作，可以向全世界亮劍了"},{"pid":"fc5e0900585b10843e14ea01a118c23835c87e68","tid":961194,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"2025高科技轉型又贏